data.description: Well-maintained 3 bed, 2 bath home in Lincoln Woods has sparkling new triple-pane windows throughout for maximum efficiency! Enjoy 3 separate living areas! Eat-in kitchen opens to back family room w/fireplace overlooking fenced backyard and patio. Formal living room offers gorgeous hardwood floors and another fireplace!  But WAIT! The rec-room in the basement is where you can have even *more* space to entertain, relax or work-out.  Backyard offers a shed and tons of low-maintenance perennials.  Upstairs walk-in closet has built-in closet system to keep you organized every day!
